
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "AboutUs";
}

<body>

    <header class="about-hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>About Drivebots</h1>
            <p>Revolutionizing the licensing process with innovation and efficiency.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="journey">
        <h2>Our Journey</h2>
        <p>A timeline of innovation and growth.</p>

        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <img src="founding.jpg" alt="Founding Drivebots" onerror="this.src='placeholder.jpg'">
                <h3>Founding Drivebots</h3>
                <span>March 18, 2025</span>
                <p>Drivebots was established in 2015 with a vision to revolutionize the licensing process.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <img src="expansion.jpg" alt="Expanding Services" onerror="this.src='placeholder.jpg'">
                <h3>Expanding Services</h3>
                <span>March 18, 2025</span>
                <p>In 2018, we expanded our offerings to include online queuing for transport services.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <img src="community.jpg" alt="Community Engagement" onerror="this.src='placeholder.jpg'">
                <h3>Community Engagement</h3>
                <span>March 18, 2025</span>
                <p>By 2021, Drivebots became actively involved in community outreach programs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="initiatives">
        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>

        <div class="initiative-box">
            <img src="accessibility.jpg" alt="Accessibility Initiatives" onerror="this.src='placeholder.jpg'">
            <div class="initiative-info">
                <h3>Accessibility Initiatives</h3>
                <p>We improve access to driving education for underserved communities.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="initiative-box">
            <img src="sustainability.jpg" alt="Sustainability Commitment" onerror="this.src='placeholder.jpg'">
            <div class="initiative-info">
                <h3>Sustainability Commitment</h3>
                <p>Promoting eco-friendly practices and reducing carbon footprints.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="initiative-box">
            <img src="partnerships.jpg" alt="Partnerships for Progress" onerror="this.src='placeholder.jpg'">
            <div class="initiative-info">
                <h3>Partnerships for Progress</h3>
                <p>Collaborating with local governments and educational institutions.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


</body>
</html>


